# ЁЯФН TransBilling Project тАФ Deep Audit Report
**Date:** 15 May 2026 | **Analyst:** Antigravity AI  
**Scope:** Backend Controllers, Models, Frontend Context & Pages  
> тЪая╕П **No code changes made.** This is a pure analysis report only.

---

## ЁЯУК Section 1: Data Fetch Limits (Hardcoded)

Ye limits production me client ko problem de sakti hain jab data zyada ho jaye.

| Location | API / Function | Limit | Risk |
|---|---|---|---|
| `admin.transport.controller.js` (L22, L32) | `GET /api/admin/transport/bills` | **200 per type** (Transport + Garage = max 400) | ЁЯФ┤ **HIGH** тАФ Admin sirf last 200 bills dekh sakta hai per type |
| `admin.garage.controller.js` (L68) | `listAllServiceBills` | **100 bills** | ЁЯФ┤ **HIGH** тАФ Old `Bill` model use karta hai (wrong model, see Bug #1) |
| `admin.users.controller.js` (L186, L193, L194) | `getUserHistory` | **100 bills, 100 trips** per user | ЁЯЯб MEDIUM тАФ Admin user detail me sirf last 100 records dikhenge |
| `admin.dashboard.controller.js` (L82) | `getRecentActivity` | **10 users** | ЁЯЯв LOW тАФ Dashboard card, intentional |
| `notification.controller.js` (L9) | `getNotifications` | **50 notifications** | ЁЯЯв LOW тАФ Acceptable for UI |
| `wallet.controller.js` (L15) | `getWallet` | **50 wallet transactions** | ЁЯЯб MEDIUM тАФ Heavy user ka purana wallet history nahi dikhega |
| `admin.users.controller.js` (L47) | `list` (User List) | **20 per page** (paginated тЬЕ) | ЁЯЯв LOW тАФ Pagination hai, theek hai |

