## ЁЯРЫ Section 2: Bugs Found

### ЁЯФ┤ Bug #1: Admin Garage Stats Wrong Model Use kar raha hai
**File:** `admin.garage.controller.js` & `admin.dashboard.controller.js`  
**Problem:** Ye dono files purana **`Bill` model** use karte hain jo lagbhag empty hai (ek legacy model hai). Actual garage bills **`GarageBill` model** me hain.

```
admin.garage.controller.js:2  тЖТ const Bill = require("../models/Bill");
admin.dashboard.controller.js:2 тЖТ const Bill = require("../models/Bill");
```

**Impact:** 
- Admin dashboard pe garage stats hamesha **0** dikhenge (ya wrong data)
- `listAllServiceBills` empty array return karega
- Admin ka revenue report galat hoga

---

### ЁЯФ┤ Bug #2: Bill Number Duplication Race Condition
**File:** `bill.controller.js` тАФ `genBillNumber()` function (L87тАУL103)  
**Problem:** Bill number generate karne ke liye pehle count kiya jata hai, phir insert. Agar do bills **ek saath** create ho (concurrent requests), dono same count dekhenge aur same bill number generate hongi.

```js
// L99: Count karo
const count = await Model.countDocuments({ owner: ownerId, billNumber: regex });
// L101: +1 kar ke number banao тАФ RACE CONDITION HERE if 2 concurrent requests
const seq = (count + 1).toString().padStart(2, '0');
```

**Impact:** Duplicate bill numbers (e.g., dono `Inv-T-2026-05`) тАФ invoice numbering corrupt ho sakti hai.

> **Note:** `TransportBill.billNumber` field me `unique` constraint nahi hai, toh DB level pe bhi check nahi hoga.

---

### ЁЯФ┤ Bug #3: CORS тАФ localhost:5173 allowed nahi hai server.js me
**File:** `server.js` (L12тАУL18)  
**Problem:** Allowed origins list me `http://localhost:5174` hai lekin frontend `.env` me `VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:4000/api` hai aur Vite by default `5173` pe run hota hai.

```js
// server.js
"http://localhost:5174",  // тЖР 5174 hai
// frontend actually 5173 pe run hota hai normally
```

**Impact:** Dev environment me CORS error aa sakta hai agar port `5173` pe run ho.

---

### ЁЯЯб Bug #4: Trip `billId` Wrong Model Reference
**File:** `backend/src/models/Trip.js` (L22)  
**Problem:** Trip model me `billId` field `Bill` model ko reference kar raha hai, lekin actual billed trips me `TransportBill` model ka ID store hota hai.

```js
billId: { type: mongoose.Schema.Types.ObjectId, ref: "Bill", ... }
// Should be ref: "TransportBill"
```

**Impact:** `.populate('billId')` call fail hoga ya wrong data return karega.

---

### ЁЯЯб Bug #5: updateBill тАФ Paid Bill Edit Guard Incomplete
**File:** `bill.controller.js` тАФ `updateBill()` (L437тАУL439)  
**Problem:** Paid bill ko edit karne se rok diya gaya hai, **lekin status ko force-update karne wala admin endpoint** (`admin.transport.controller.js:updateBillStatus`) me koi restriction nahi hai. Admin galti se paid bill ko unpaid bhi kar sakta hai.

---

### ЁЯЯб Bug #6: GarageBill `status` vs `paymentMode` mismatch
**File:** `bill.controller.js` тАФ `createBill()` (L352)  
**Problem:** Garage bill create karte waqt `paymentMode` aur `status` alag-alag calculate ho rahe hain jo conflict de sakta hai.

```js
paymentMode: (status === "paid" || paymentMode === "paid") ? "paid" : ...
status: status || "unpaid",
```

**Impact:** Ek bill ka `status="unpaid"` aur `paymentMode="paid"` ho sakta hai simultaneously тАФ inconsistent data.

---

### ЁЯЯб Bug #7: Subscription Expiry Check Only on Frontend
**File:** `frontend/src/router/ProtectedRoute.jsx` (L66тАУL69)  
**Problem:** Subscription expiry check sirf **frontend** pe hai. Backend routes me koi middleware nahi hai jo expired subscription wale user ko bills banane se roke.

**Impact:** Agar koi user directly Postman se API call kare with valid JWT, subscription expire hone ke baad bhi bills/trips create kar sakta hai.

---

### ЁЯЯб Bug #8: Delete Bill тАФ Transaction Auto-Delete Nahi Hoti
**File:** `bill.controller.js` тАФ `deleteBill()` (L501тАУL522)  
**Problem:** Jab ek paid bill delete ki jati hai, us se associated `Transaction` record delete nahi hoti. Finance ledger me orphan income entries reh jaati hain.

---

### ЁЯЯб Bug #9: Trip Delete тАФ billed Trip Delete Possible
**File:** `transport.controller.js` тАФ `deleteTrip()` (L241тАУL248)  
**Problem:** Already-billed trip ko delete karne se koi nahi rokta. Agar trip delete ho gayi lekin bill exist kare, bill me dangling trip IDs aa jaayenge.

---

## тЪая╕П Section 3: Gaps & Missing Features

### Gap #1: Bill Number Sequence Reset per Year (Bug Risk in Year Change)
**File:** `bill.controller.js` тАФ `genBillNumber()` (L88)  
Year January 1 ko change hoga, sequence reset hogar to `01`. But agar DB me koi purani matching entry year-old regex se match ho toh sequence wrong start ho sakta hai.

---

### Gap #2: No Rate Limiting on OTP Endpoint
**File:** `backend/utils/otpStore.js` + `auth.controller.js`  
Koi bhi number pe unlimited OTP requests bhej sakta hai. No throttling / rate limiting on `/api/auth/send-otp`. SMS cost unlimited ho sakti hai.

---

### Gap #3: Party Deletion тАФ Linked Bills Orphan Ho Jaate Hain
**File:** `party.controller.js` тАФ `deleteParty()`  
Party delete karne se linked bills me `party` field null ho jaata hai. Koi cascading delete ya validation nahi hai.

---

### Gap #4: In-Memory OTP Store тАФ Server Restart pe OTPs Lost
**File:** `backend/utils/otpStore.js`  
OTPs server memory me hain. Server restart hone par **all active OTPs expire** ho jaate hain. Production me Redis chahiye.

---

### Gap #5: Admin Bills View Paginated Nahi Hai (Frontend)
**File:** `admin.transport.controller.js`  
Admin `/api/admin/transport/bills` call karta hai jo max 200+200 = 400 bills ek saath return karta hai. Koi pagination nahi hai. Heavy memory usage on both server and browser.

---

### Gap #6: Finance Transactions тАФ No Pagination
**File:** `finance.controller.js` тАФ `listTransactions()`  
**ALL** transactions ek API call me return hoti hain тАФ koi pagination, koi limit nahi. Heavy user ke liye thousands of records ek saath load honge.

---

### Gap #7: Parties List тАФ No Pagination
**File:** `party.controller.js` тАФ `listParties()`  
Saari parties ek saath load hoti hain. Koi pagination nahi.

---

### Gap #8: Garage Vehicle List тАФ No Pagination
**File:** `garage.controller.js` тАФ `listVehicles()` & `garageVehicle.controller.js`  
All vehicles at once тАФ no limit, no pagination.

---

### Gap #9: Notification Cleanup тАФ Old Notifications DB Me Accumulate Honge
**File:** `notification.controller.js`  
Notifications sirf manually delete hoti hain. Koi TTL index ya auto-expiry nahi hai. Heavy usage me lakhon unread notifications DB me jam jaayenge.

---

### Gap #10: Wallet Transactions Limited to 50 (User Side)
**File:** `wallet.controller.js`  
User sirf last 50 wallet transactions dekh sakta hai. Purani transactions permanently invisible hain.

---

