| Feature | Status |
|---|---|
| Bill generation (user side) | тЬЕ No limit тАФ unlimited bills generate ho sakte hain |
| Bill listing (user side) | тЬЕ No limit тАФ `listBills` ALL bills return karta hai without limit |
| Vehicle creation (transport) | тЬЕ No limit тАФ `allowedVehicles` = 0 = Unlimited |
| Vehicle creation (garage) | тЬЕ No limit enforced |
| Trip creation | тЬЕ No limit |
| Party creation | тЬЕ No limit |
| Bill search/filter (frontend) | тЬЕ Client-side, works on full fetched list |
| Bill sorting (frontend) | тЬЕ Works correctly |
| OTP system (user side) | тЬЕ Working with real OTPs for non-test numbers |
| Subscription enforcement | тЬЕ Frontend guard working |

