## ЁЯУЛ Summary Table тАФ Priority Action List

| Priority | Issue | Fix Needed |
|---|---|---|
| ЁЯФ┤ P1 | Admin garage stats use wrong `Bill` model | Replace `Bill` with `GarageBill` |
| ЁЯФ┤ P1 | Bill number race condition / no unique constraint | Add DB unique index + atomic counter |
| ЁЯФ┤ P1 | CORS localhost port mismatch | Add `localhost:5173` to allowedOrigins |
| ЁЯЯб P2 | Trip `billId` wrong model ref | Change `ref: "Bill"` to `ref: "TransportBill"` |
| ЁЯЯб P2 | No backend subscription expiry middleware | Add auth middleware for subscription check |
| ЁЯЯб P2 | Delete bill doesn't delete transaction | Add transaction cleanup on bill delete |
| ЁЯЯб P2 | Finance transactions no pagination | Add limit/skip to `listTransactions` |
| ЁЯЯб P2 | No OTP rate limiting | Add rate limiter on `/send-otp` route |
| ЁЯЯв P3 | Admin bills view 200 limit | Add proper pagination to admin bills API |
| ЁЯЯв P3 | In-memory OTP store | Migrate to Redis for production |
| ЁЯЯв P3 | Party/vehicle lists no pagination | Add pagination |
| ЁЯЯв P3 | Notification auto-cleanup | Add MongoDB TTL index on notifications |
